<subSubSection id="3796656070D9FF3FFF23EF108F23FE0C" pageId="167" pageNumber="168" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="7F3336EB70D9FF3FFF23EF108F23FE0C" blockId="167.[151,1436,289,458]" pageId="167" pageNumber="168">
<emphasis id="4DF8EAF970D9FF3FFF23EF108B44FE9B" bold="true" box="[199,335,325,350]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="167" pageNumber="168" reason="1">Comments.</emphasis>
This species, based on a series of impression fossil queens, is only tentatively placed in 
<taxonomicName id="B88C4D6870D9FF3FFA92EF138B07FE44" baseAuthorityName="Shattuck" baseAuthorityYear="1990" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Iridomyrmex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="167" pageNumber="168" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="4DF8EAF970D9FF3FFA92EF138B07FE44" italics="true" pageId="167" pageNumber="168">Iridomyrmex</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as very little morphological detail is available. It is unlikely that this species is related to modern 
<taxonomicName id="B88C4D6870D9FF3FFA92EF3F8B00FE60" baseAuthorityName="Shattuck" baseAuthorityYear="1990" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Iridomyrmex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="167" pageNumber="168" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="4DF8EAF970D9FF3FFA92EF3F8B00FE60" italics="true" pageId="167" pageNumber="168">Iridomyrmex</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but so little information is available that it is extremely difficult to determine its true relationships. As such it is retained in 
<taxonomicName id="B88C4D6870D9FF3FFE9BEFE4881BFE0C" baseAuthorityName="Shattuck" baseAuthorityYear="1990" box="[383,528,433,457]" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Iridomyrmex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="167" pageNumber="168" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="4DF8EAF970D9FF3FFE9BEFE4881BFE0C" box="[383,528,433,457]" italics="true" pageId="167" pageNumber="168">Iridomyrmex</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as 
<emphasis id="4DF8EAF970D9FF3FFDD1EFE788DBFE0C" box="[565,720,433,457]" italics="true" pageId="167" pageNumber="168">incertae sedis</emphasis>
with strong reservations that it actually belongs here.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
